1
00:00:41,359 --> 00:00:42,359
Father, please listen to me.

2
00:00:42,359 --> 00:00:43,039
Get out of here!

3
00:00:54,079 --> 00:00:55,759
Father, I can explain.

4
00:00:55,759 --> 00:00:56,600
You know that.

5
00:00:57,240 --> 00:00:58,079
All these years,

6
00:00:58,119 --> 00:00:59,359
I haven't been able to let Siqi go.

7
00:00:59,719 --> 00:01:01,359
So when Siqi came back from the US,

8
00:01:01,359 --> 00:01:02,640
we got back together.

9
00:01:02,880 --> 00:01:03,799
But don't worry.

10
00:01:03,799 --> 00:01:05,400
I will never call off my engagement to Jiang Lai.

11
00:01:05,640 --> 00:01:07,400
So you two were sneaking around

12
00:01:08,719 --> 00:01:10,000
just to have an affair.

13
00:01:11,040 --> 00:01:13,439
We feared Jiang Lai would make a scene.

14
00:01:13,879 --> 00:01:15,040
You know what she's like.

15
00:01:16,799 --> 00:01:18,599
You really are a sentimental fool.

16
00:01:18,599 --> 00:01:19,280
I...

17
00:01:19,560 --> 00:01:21,400
Enough. No need to explain.

18
00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:23,840
I understand.

19
00:01:31,879 --> 00:01:33,120
Other than this,

20
00:01:33,439 --> 00:01:34,920
is there anything else you're hiding from me?

21
00:01:35,159 --> 00:01:35,879
Nothing else.

22
00:01:41,519 --> 00:01:42,280
Take care, Father.

23
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:57,280
Welcome.

24
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:58,879
Sorry, Mr. Sheng.

25
00:01:58,920 --> 00:02:00,799
Those two were just in Room 608.

26
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,039
Sheng Shizhong is downstairs.

27
00:02:13,039 --> 00:02:14,280
He's probably coming up any minute.

28
00:02:14,439 --> 00:02:15,159
Then...

29
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:16,400
What do we do?

30
00:02:17,639 --> 00:02:18,400
Come with me.

31
00:02:21,159 --> 00:02:21,879
Where?

32
00:02:26,199 --> 00:02:28,199
Sheng Shizhong should have his guard down for now.

33
00:02:28,319 --> 00:02:29,879
Then the Bidding session

34
00:02:30,759 --> 00:02:31,560
needs to happen ASAP.

35
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:43,919
Thanks for bailing me out today.

36
00:02:44,039 --> 00:02:45,759
Or Sheng Shizhong would've exposed me.

37
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:47,800
No need.

38
00:02:48,479 --> 00:02:49,280
Helping you

39
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:50,680
is really helping myself, isn't it?

40
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,120
What are you doing here?

41
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,319
I know

42
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:04,960
I did things you can't forgive.

43
00:03:05,039 --> 00:03:06,599
But I hope you'll hear me out.

44
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:07,840
Hear what?

45
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:09,319
How you plotted

46
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:11,599
to take Benevolent Medical shares from me?

47
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:12,879
It's not like that, Siqi.

48
00:03:12,879 --> 00:03:13,280
Listen to me.

49
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:14,680
You didn't know what it was like back then.

50
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:16,319
I had to take the shares from you

51
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:18,240
to win Sheng Shizhong's trust.

52
00:03:19,879 --> 00:03:20,960
Then you got what you wanted.

53
00:03:21,759 --> 00:03:22,639
Congratulations.

54
00:03:23,319 --> 00:03:24,919
I never wanted to hurt you, Siqi.

55
00:03:25,479 --> 00:03:26,280
Please believe me.

56
00:03:26,599 --> 00:03:27,960
One day I'll return it all in full,

57
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:29,439
everything I took from you.

58
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,360
Just treat it like I borrowed it.

59
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:33,199
You're asking me to lend you my shares?

60
00:03:34,639 --> 00:03:35,960
Then can you return them tomorrow?

61
00:03:36,199 --> 00:03:36,960
You still think

62
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:38,400
I'll believe anything you say?

63
00:03:38,719 --> 00:03:39,520
You knew perfectly well

64
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:41,319
how important those shares were to me.

65
00:03:41,639 --> 00:03:44,120
Siqi, having this money right now

66
00:03:44,159 --> 00:03:46,159
is more useful than keeping those shares.

67
00:03:46,159 --> 00:03:47,039
Useful for what?

68
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:48,280
You can study abroad.

69
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,719
Chase your dream of being a reporter.

70
00:03:49,879 --> 00:03:51,599
Do anything you want.

71
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:54,719
Instead of being trapped in this dead end.

72
00:03:57,919 --> 00:03:58,719
One year.

73
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:00,879
I only need one year.

74
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,319
We'll both build up our strength,

75
00:04:02,319 --> 00:04:04,000
then take Sheng Shizhong down together.

76
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,719
You're going after your dad?

77
00:04:09,719 --> 00:04:10,319
Yes.

78
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:12,879
I know it sounds crazy,

79
00:04:13,039 --> 00:04:14,599
but only by bringing him down for good

80
00:04:14,759 --> 00:04:16,040
will all of this end.

81
00:04:16,639 --> 00:04:18,079
Right now, only you can help me.

82
00:04:29,279 --> 00:04:30,759
Can I trust you again?

83
00:04:39,399 --> 00:04:40,720
Thanks for trusting me.

84
00:04:43,199 --> 00:04:45,240
Honestly, I don't know why,

85
00:04:46,439 --> 00:04:48,240
but it's so easy to trust you.

86
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:50,480
It's like, deep down,

87
00:04:50,959 --> 00:04:52,279
there's this strange feeling.

88
00:05:00,639 --> 00:05:01,639
After you came back,

89
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:03,079
have you seen Zhang Xiaobei?

90
00:05:03,639 --> 00:05:04,360
I have.

91
00:05:04,839 --> 00:05:05,639
Then you two...

92
00:05:05,839 --> 00:05:07,079
There's no chance for us anymore.

93
00:05:07,279 --> 00:05:08,839
We've both changed a lot.

94
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:10,839
And we both have new lives now.

95
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:13,720
We're good friends now, I guess.

96
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,120
Life is a long road.

97
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,480
Maybe one day,

98
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:21,079
things will change back again.

99
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,839
Or maybe one day,

100
00:05:25,639 --> 00:05:27,079
I'll meet someone even better.

101
00:05:36,199 --> 00:05:37,879
Why is there no one here?

102
00:05:38,759 --> 00:05:39,639
I don't know.

103
00:05:43,399 --> 00:05:44,360
Why are you here?

104
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:48,160
Stop waiting.

105
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:50,399
No developers are coming.

106
00:05:51,519 --> 00:05:52,360
Why?

107
00:05:53,439 --> 00:05:54,720
Sheng Shizhong put the word out.

108
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:57,000
Whoever takes the West District development project

109
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,720
is taking on all of Prosperity Group.

110
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:00,759
This again.

111
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:02,439
Plus,

112
00:06:02,839 --> 00:06:04,519
Prosperity Group will put up one billion.

113
00:06:05,079 --> 00:06:06,120
In the North District,

114
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:08,079
they'll create 100,000 jobs

115
00:06:08,079 --> 00:06:09,720
in a digitally integrated industrial park.

116
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,360
Together with the East District,

117
00:06:11,839 --> 00:06:14,480
they'll build a digitally integrated city of the future.

118
00:06:15,079 --> 00:06:16,680
If this Bidding session fails,

119
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:18,600
all our efforts will be for nothing.

120
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:21,000
Then what do we do?

121
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,879
At this rate, no developer

122
00:06:22,879 --> 00:06:24,160
will be willing to come here.

123
00:06:24,399 --> 00:06:25,399
So now we just

124
00:06:26,399 --> 00:06:28,079
sit and watch it all fall apart?

125
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:30,319
There's only one person who can save us now.

126
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:32,639
Who?

127
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:35,680
Jiang Lai.

128
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,079
So far,

129
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:42,319
not a single developer has bid.

130
00:06:42,639 --> 00:06:43,759
If this keeps up,

131
00:06:43,879 --> 00:06:45,639
the over 6 billion we invested before

132
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:47,240
will all go down the drain.

133
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,000
You...

134
00:06:48,199 --> 00:06:50,160
When did you team up with Lin Siqi?

135
00:06:50,399 --> 00:06:51,680
It's a long story.

136
00:06:51,879 --> 00:06:52,800
So you're saying

137
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:54,720
you were in touch with Lin Siqi all along.

138
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:59,319
Jiang Lai, don't get the wrong idea.

139
00:06:59,319 --> 00:07:01,439
Sheng Yuanzhou and I are just partners right now.

140
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:02,240
I don't want to hear it from you.

141
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:03,160
I want to hear it from him.

142
00:07:03,759 --> 00:07:04,879
Actually, this plan

143
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:06,800
started a year ago, when Siqi left.

144
00:07:06,879 --> 00:07:07,959
It was already in motion then.

145
00:07:08,079 --> 00:07:10,319
So you secretly kept in touch for a year.

146
00:07:10,519 --> 00:07:11,720
Siqi and I teaming up

147
00:07:11,879 --> 00:07:13,759
was just to bring Sheng Shizhong down.

148
00:07:13,839 --> 00:07:14,639
As for the rest,

149
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:16,920
I can't Reveal everything to you yet.

150
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,519
But please believe me.

151
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:20,439
I've always remembered what I promised you.

152
00:07:20,519 --> 00:07:21,720
I'll never let you down.

153
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:25,600
I really need your help right now.

154
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:26,480
The only one who can help me

155
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:27,639
is you.

156
00:07:36,160 --> 00:07:38,199
My goal is to marry into the Sheng family.

157
00:07:38,199 --> 00:07:39,480
To be the Sheng family's daughter-in-law.

158
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,800
If Wanli Construction

159
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,800
takes the West District development project,

160
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,879
that means openly going against Sheng Shizhong.

161
00:07:45,079 --> 00:07:46,319
Can I still marry into the Sheng family?

162
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:47,800
I'm not that stupid.

163
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:49,399
You'd better find someone else.

164
00:07:52,439 --> 00:07:53,240
Jiang Lai.

165
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:59,120
Do you want to stay Dependent on others

166
00:07:59,439 --> 00:08:00,720
and be someone's lackey forever?

167
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:04,800
Gladly.

168
00:08:04,959 --> 00:08:06,160
You're just putting on an act,

169
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:07,399
like you don't care about anything,

170
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:08,720
like all you care about is profit.

171
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:11,839
Don't act like you know me so well.

172
00:08:13,759 --> 00:08:14,560
Jiang Lai.

173
00:08:16,079 --> 00:08:17,600
Deep down, you're kind.

174
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:19,959
That's why you became Jiang Lai.

175
00:08:20,319 --> 00:08:21,519
It's not that you owe the Jiang family.

176
00:08:22,439 --> 00:08:24,240
It's that Jiang Lai chose you.

177
00:08:31,199 --> 00:08:33,039
Enough. Quit lecturing me.

178
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:41,279
What do we do now?

179
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:43,639
It's fine. Give her some time.

180
00:08:45,519 --> 00:08:47,480
I believe she'll be on our side.

181
00:08:57,399 --> 00:08:59,120
The deadline's almost here.

182
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,840
Do you think Jiang Lai will come?

183
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:01,879
Wait a little longer.

184
00:09:03,759 --> 00:09:04,960
But what if...

185
00:09:13,279 --> 00:09:14,600
I knew you'd come.

186
00:09:16,279 --> 00:09:17,360
I can help you.

187
00:09:17,679 --> 00:09:18,799
But I have a condition.

188
00:09:30,679 --> 00:09:31,279
Name it.

189
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,879
Put your Key of Fate up as collateral

190
00:09:36,879 --> 00:09:37,799
and leave it with me.

191
00:09:39,159 --> 00:09:40,000
No problem.

192
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:49,879
Let's wish today's press event

193
00:09:49,879 --> 00:09:50,960
a complete success.

194
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:53,519
Lastly, thanks to all the media for coming.

195
00:09:53,639 --> 00:09:54,440
Thank you, everyone.

196
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:07,799
Pleasure doing business.

197
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:08,759
Pleasure doing business.

198
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:30,600
I've kept my promise.

199
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:33,840
Now it's your turn to keep yours.

200
00:10:36,759 --> 00:10:38,240
Sneaking around behind my back,

201
00:10:38,559 --> 00:10:39,840
even starting a company together.

202
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,440
Then when something happens, you come to me.

203
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,120
You only want me when you need something

204
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:45,240
and toss me aside when you don't.

205
00:10:45,879 --> 00:10:47,120
No way I'm helping you.

206
00:10:50,519 --> 00:10:51,240
Jiang Lai.

207
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:58,679
What is the Key of Fate?

208
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:01,200
You don't need to know that.

209
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:04,039
Just get it from Sheng Yuanzhou.

210
00:11:04,039 --> 00:11:04,960
That's all.

211
00:11:05,799 --> 00:11:07,000
And what's in it for me?

212
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:09,120
Haven't you always wanted to marry into the Sheng family?

213
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:10,759
I promise you,

214
00:11:11,519 --> 00:11:14,320
you'll be the Sheng family's only daughter-in-law.

215
00:11:14,799 --> 00:11:15,759
That was before.

216
00:11:16,399 --> 00:11:18,960
Now that you've come in person,

217
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:21,360
I'm afraid the price is going up.

218
00:11:23,639 --> 00:11:24,600
What do you want?

219
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:27,720
Five percent of Prosperity Group's shares.

220
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:29,879
You're asking for a lot.

221
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:31,840
Even though I don't know

222
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:33,480
what the Key of Fate is,

223
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:35,240
still,

224
00:11:35,519 --> 00:11:38,600
since it brought Chairman Sheng out in person,

225
00:11:38,919 --> 00:11:40,840
it must be worth a lot.

226
00:11:41,039 --> 00:11:41,960
Am I right?

227
00:11:43,200 --> 00:11:43,840
Fine.

228
00:11:44,679 --> 00:11:46,639
If you really can get the Key of Fate,

229
00:11:46,879 --> 00:11:48,200
I'll give you five percent

230
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:49,480
of Prosperity Group's shares.

231
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:51,080
Deal.

232
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:17,799
Where did everyone go?

233
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:24,679
Zhang Xiaobei.

234
00:12:26,039 --> 00:12:26,879
Why are you here?

235
00:12:28,759 --> 00:12:30,000
I'm waiting for you.

236
00:12:33,519 --> 00:12:34,639
Zhang Xiaobei.

237
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:40,320
Zhang Xiaobei!

238
00:12:41,279 --> 00:12:43,240
Why did you steal my life?
